<br>
I would like to start a thread here to see what people consider as &quot;average&quot; gear for a lvl 60 magician. Please post your ideas.<br>
<br>
On a side note, I find it sad that magician, who NEVER were dependant on mana really now suddenly HAVE to get upgrades to cast their spells. I know some of you see gear dependency as good, but IMO gear should IMPROVE our abilites, not ENABLE them.<br>
<br>
Izudin<br>
