<br>
If you got that kinda cash go for it, they are good items.  If not try picking up a few of the following.  Maidens Eye has the neckalce of magikot and earring of magikot and hoop of magikot drops with pretty decent rate.  All are decent mage gear and easy to get.  Stein of moggok is an obvious one.  Earring of everfount is another good item with hp mana on it, if you dont want to hit maidens.<br>
<br>
Really, if you want advice we need to know what you have.  If you need mana get your int to 200+ first, then work on plus mana gear.<br>
<br>
